<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><img src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C000000395ip&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f"></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Hey&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">As one of our valued NCS Ambassadors, we just wanted to let you know about some amazing opportunities you can still get involved </span>in!</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font color="#cc0000" size="4"><b>1. NCS Ambassador Phone Party:</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial"><b>Get trained</b> on top customer service tips</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Get on the phone</b> to upcoming NCS 2016 participants</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Use your experience</b> to get them excited for the summer!</font></li><li><font face="arial">Help yourself earn a <b>TCS Award</b>! [LINK TO TCS AWARDS PAGE ON LOCAL WEBSITE]&nbsp;</font></li></ul></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">The Phone Party will be happening during the next half-term on <b>[DATE] from [TIMES] in [GENERAL AREA]</b>. If you're interested, fill in <b>this form</b> [LINK TO GOOGLE FORM] and we'll give you a call to discuss it further.</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font color="#cc0000" size="4"><b>2. NCS 2016 Information Evenings:&nbsp;</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial"><b>Share you NCS experience</b> with the parents/guardians of upcoming 2016 participants</font></li><li><font face="arial">Let them know all about <b>your time on the programme</b> and what their young person can expect</font></li><li><font face="arial">Help yourself earn a <b>TCS Award</b>!&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: arial;">[LINK TO TCS AWARDS PAGE ON LOCAL WEBSITE]&nbsp;</span></li></ul><div><font face="arial">Information Evenings take place on a regular basis throughout the summer. If you're interested in attending one or more as an NCS Ambassador, email<b> [SALES NCS AMBASSADOR LEAD EMAIL]</b> for more information.</font></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Thanks to everyone who has helped spread the word of NCS already this year. We hope to see you again soon!</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b>The Challenge Society</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div>]]></td>
